Name: Cuyo
About the game: Cuyo is a relaxing, small platformer. Relax and play with relax mode or take a small challenge in normal mode. Cuyo is the first in a series of 3. Platform elements: Wall-jump, double-jump, wall-cling, exiting obstacles and enemies. Beauty and peace: The game was design to bring a beautiful and relaxing experience while increasing the challenge as the player goes. Can you find the hidden poem?
